== 2012 program == [[File:Celebration of Light Brazil 2012 20.JPG|thumb|The 2012 Brazil show]] The 2012 Honda Celebration of Light was saw teams from Vietnam and Brazil as newcomers, while the Italian team of Pirotecnica Soldi was more established.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/Celebration+Light+unites+Brazil+Italy+Vietnam+trifecta/6989706/story.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120730112942/http://www.vancouversun.com/Celebration%2BLight%2Bunites%2BBrazil%2BItaly%2BVietnam%2Btrifecta/6989706/story.html |dead-url=yes |archive-date=July 30, 2012 |title=Vancouver skies to come alive tonight - Celebration of Light unites Brazil, Italy and Vietnam in a new trifecta |date=July 30, 2012 |publisher=Vancouver Sun |first1=Manori |last1=Ravindran |df= }}</ref> Canada did not participate for the first time in six years as producers of the event had been looking for new countries to compete from each continent for the next three years.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://vancouverisawesome.com/2012/07/27/honda-celebration-of-light-fireworks-barge-tour/#more-135088|title=Honda Celebration of Light fireworks barge tour|author=Brice Ferre|date=July 27, 2012|work=VIAwesome}}</ref> The 2012 competition winner was Italy.
